@startuml
!theme plain
title PromptFlow React Streaming Chatbot - Deployment Diagram

node "Client Browser" {
    [React Application] as ReactApp
    [Chatbot Component] as ChatbotComp
}

node "Web Server" {
    [ASP.NET Core API] as WebAPI
    [ChatController] as Controller
}

cloud "Azure Cloud" {
    node "PromptFlow Service" {
        [PromptFlow Runtime] as PromptFlow
    }
    
    node "Azure OpenAI Service" {
        [GPT Model] as GPT
    }
}

database "Configuration" {
    [API Keys] as Keys
    [Endpoints] as Endpoints
}

' Deployment relationships
ReactApp --> ChatbotComp : contains
ChatbotComp --> WebAPI : HTTPS\n(text/event-stream)

WebAPI --> Controller : routes
Controller --> PromptFlow : HTTPS\n(Bearer token)

PromptFlow --> GPT : API calls

Controller --> Keys : reads
Controller --> Endpoints : uses

' Network protocols
ChatbotComp --> WebAPI : POST /api/Chat
WebAPI --> ChatbotComp : SSE Stream

Controller --> PromptFlow : POST /score
PromptFlow --> Controller : SSE Stream

note right of ReactApp
  Runs in user's browser
  Handles UI and streaming
end note

note right of WebAPI
  Backend proxy server
  Handles authentication
  and request forwarding
end note

note right of PromptFlow
  Hosted AI service
  Processes chat requests
  Returns streaming responses
end note

note bottom of Keys
  Requires configuration:
  - API Key for PromptFlow
  - PromptFlow service URI
end note

@enduml